{{ROLE}} The user has invoked `/teamLimit [n]`.

Set the maximum number of Sub AIs that can run simultaneously.

---

## Step 1 — Parse Argument

The user may have provided a number after `/teamLimit`, e.g. `/teamLimit 8`.

- If a number is provided: use that as the new limit
- If no number is provided: show current limit and ask user for a value

```
현재 Team Limit: [current teamLimit]
현재 가동 중인 Sub AI: [current count]

새로운 한도를 숫자로 입력해주세요.
```

---

## Step 2 — Validate

- Minimum allowed value: 1
- If the new limit is LESS than the current number of active Sub AIs, warn the user:
  > "⚠️ 현재 가동 중인 Sub AI([count]개)보다 낮은 값입니다. 일부 Sub AI가 다음 작업 완료 후 종료됩니다. 계속하시겠습니까? (y/n)"

---

## Step 3 — Update State

Update `doc/company_state.json`:
- Set `"teamLimit": [n]`

Update `doc/AI_list.txt` Team Status section:
- `Team Limit` → new value
- `Available Slot` → teamLimit - current active Sub AI count

---

## Step 4 — Report to User

```
⚙️ Team Limit 변경

이전: [old limit]  →  새로운 한도: [n]
현재 가동 Sub AI: [current count]
가용 슬롯: [available]
```
